title: A Minimal Homepage
text: This is a minimal quarto homepage.

title: How To Do This
text:
Install R: https://cran.r-project.org/
Install RStudio: https://posit.co/download/rstudio-desktop/
Install the quarto suite: https://quarto.org/
Register GitHub: https://github.com/

Start RStudio.

Choose: File and New Project
Choose: Project Type “Quarto Website”
